        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This portable silver anvil has a narrow hoop on one end, through which a long, sturdy chain has been strung. Torag's Silver Anvil can be wielded as a +3 @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Holy] @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Flaming (Greater)]{Greater Flaming} greater striking silver meteor hammer.</p>\n<p>Outside of combat, the anvil can be used with a hammer as an incredibly effective portable forge, heating up the metal to be forged without a furnace and granting a +3 item bonus to Crafting checks involving metalworking.</p>\n<p>When you use the anvil to successfully Repair a metal item, the item recovers an additional 10 Hit Points (or an additional 20 on a critical success).</p>"
